{"tid":1135341,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"上到嚟讀書識朋友 搵個真係當你朋友係咪咁難？","createTime":"2019-05-02T08:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T17:27:43.000Z","uid":201598,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b9199a2095024552c496f01300ae5cf068abf0","tid":1135341,"uid":201598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"發覺上到嚟之後，同中學嗰陣完全唔同，本身見大家啱傾咁就做朋友，自問自己都攞個心出嚟交朋友，點知漸漸就好似大家變咗互相競爭嘅人咁，甚至臨尾因為project 而搞到友盡咁樣，大家開始有唔同諗法嘅出現又唔肯去解決，話晒曾經都係朋友點解可以因為小事而搞到反晒面咁。其實真係好想搵一班可以並肩作戰一齊奮鬥讀書嘅朋友，但係而家下一個sem應該要自己一個了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究竟搵個真係當你朋友又唔反面，一齊讀書嘅朋友係咪咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84386fb56b312728c6961f4f507c9448e658a1f4","tid":1135341,"uid":146092,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"你邊度上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ff1b830fcd75d1dbbf8672baf86addf2444079","tid":1135341,"uid":200975,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"落返去"},{"pid":"2246392ac23f09893c79406f4c9575498f711b7a","tid":1135341,"uid":39215,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"地府上黎?"},{"pid":"39cdb0f34cc6b52c0b3b0311321690aa96f6e859","tid":1135341,"uid":203657,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"道不同 不相為謀"},{"pid":"0850b8cadb5da2ce9f6bd7f2564e8dcd8795d5d6","tid":1135341,"uid":202630,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T10:10:54.000Z","msg":"咁不如落返去啦 吾撚洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor